Entity Hub Open Project
=======================

Copyright (C) 2025 Entity Hub Contributors

DESCRIPTION
===========

Entity Hub is a flexible entity management system with robust authentication,
authorization, and audit logging. It provides a modern web application for
managing abstract entities (clients, contracts, categories, etc.) with a focus
on security and extensibility.

Built with:
  - Go (backend API server)
  - React (frontend)
  - PostgreSQL (database)
  - Docker (deployment)

